snippet.title: Hololive Isekai v0.2
snippet.description:
The idols of Hololive have been mysteriously sucked into an alternate dimension, where dangerous monsters roam. It feels too much like a game, but no time to think about that! They have to save each other, battle monsters and escape back to Hololive HQ, so they can return to putting smiles on their fans' faces!

Fan game made by Hololive Isekai Team
Download: https://drweam.itch.io/hololive-isekai

We are not affiliated with Hololive Productions or COVER Corp.
This is a non-commercial fan-made game meant for the fans.
All rights reserved to the respective owners.
